{{! Subject: Draft minutes ready for review — {{boardName}}, {{meetingDate}} }}
<h2 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:22px;color:#1a3a6b;font-weight:normal;">
  Draft Minutes Ready for Review
</h2>

<p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;">{{townName}}</p>

<p style="margin:0 0 16px;">
  Hi {{recipientName}},
</p>

<p style="margin:0 0 16px;">
  The draft minutes from the <strong>{{boardName}}</strong> meeting on
  <strong>{{meetingDate}}</strong> are ready for your review.
</p>

<p style="margin:0 0 24px;">
  Please review the draft and submit any corrections or approve the minutes using the link below.
</p>

<!-- CTA Button -->
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 24px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color:#1a3a6b;border-radius:4px;padding:12px 28px;">
      <a href="{{reviewUrl}}"
         style="color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;display:block;">
        Review Draft Minutes
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;">
  This is a required action for board members of the {{boardName}}.
  Minutes must be reviewed before they can be formally approved at the next meeting.
</p>
